  "root_text": {
    "iti20:0.1": "Itivuttaka 20 ",
    "iti20:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti20:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti20:0.4": "Paduṭṭhacittasutta ",
    "iti20:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti20:2.1": "“Idhāhaṁ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṁ puggalaṁ paduṭṭhacittaṁ evaṁ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: ",
    "iti20:2.2": "‘imamhi cāyaṁ samaye puggalo kālaṁ kareyya yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ niraye’. ",
    "iti20:2.3": "Taṁ kissa hetu? ",
    "iti20:2.4": "Cittaṁ hissa, bhikkhave, paduṭṭhaṁ. ",
    "iti20:2.5": "Cetopadosahetu kho pana, bhikkhave, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṁ maraṇā apāyaṁ duggatiṁ vinipātaṁ nirayaṁ upapajjantī”ti. ",
    "iti20:2.6": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti20:2.7": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti20:3.1": "“Paduṭṭhacittaṁ ñatvāna, ",
    "iti20:3.2": "ekaccaṁ idha puggalaṁ; ",
    "iti20:3.3": "Etamatthañca byākāsi, ",
    "iti20:3.4": "buddho bhikkhūna santike. ",
    "iti20:4.1": "Imamhi cāyaṁ samaye, ",
    "iti20:4.2": "kālaṁ kayirātha puggalo; ",
    "iti20:4.3": "Nirayaṁ upapajjeyya, ",
    "iti20:4.4": "cittaṁ hissa padūsitaṁ. ",
    "iti20:5.1": "Yathā haritvā nikkhipeyya, ",
    "iti20:5.2": "evamevaṁ tathāvidho; ",
    "iti20:5.3": "Cetopadosahetu hi, ",
    "iti20:5.4": "sattā gacchanti duggatin”ti. ",
    "iti20:6.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti20:6.2": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "iti20:6.3": "Dutiyo vaggo. ",
    "iti20:7.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "iti20:7.1": "Moho kodho atha makkho, ",
    "iti20:7.2": "Vijjā taṇhā sekhaduve ca; ",
    "iti20:7.3": "Bhedo sāmaggipuggalo, ",
    "iti20:7.4": "Vaggamāhu dutiyanti vuccatīti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti20:0.1": "So It Was Said 20 ",
    "iti20:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti20:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti20:0.4": "A Corrupted Mind ",
    "iti20:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti20:2.1": "“Mendicants, when I’ve comprehended the mind of an individual whose mind is corrupted, I understand: ",
    "iti20:2.2": "‘If this individual were to die right now, they would be placed in hell as if delivered there.’ ",
    "iti20:2.3": "Why is that? ",
    "iti20:2.4": "Because their mind is corrupted. ",
    "iti20:2.5": "Corruption of mind is the reason why some sentient beings, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” ",
    "iti20:2.6": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti20:2.7": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti20:3.1": "“Knowing an individual’s ",
    "iti20:3.2": "corrupted mind, ",
    "iti20:3.3": "the Buddha explained this matter ",
    "iti20:3.4": "in the mendicants’ presence. ",
    "iti20:4.1": "If that individual ",
    "iti20:4.2": "were to die at this time, ",
    "iti20:4.3": "they’d be reborn in hell, ",
    "iti20:4.4": "for their mind is corrupted. ",
    "iti20:5.1": "That sort is cast down as surely ",
    "iti20:5.2": "as if they’d been carried off and put there. ",
    "iti20:5.3": "For corruption of mind is the reason ",
    "iti20:5.4": "sentient beings go to a bad place.” ",
    "iti20:6.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti20:7.3": "Bhedo sāmaggipuggalo → mūhā kāmasekkhaduve; bhedasāmaggapuggalo ca (bj, mr); mohakodhā atha makkho mohakāmā sekkhā duve; bhedamodā puggalo ca (sya-all, pts-vp-pli1) "
  },
